# Write a Letter to Your Mayor

## Please provide your "first and last name," "neighborhood, borough," and the date you are writing this letter.

<hr width="100%" style="height:10px;color:red;background-color:lightgrey">

The \${strName}.

```{ojs}
//| echo: false
//| 
viewof strName = Inputs.text({label: "Your Name"})

viewof strNeighborhood = Inputs.text({label: "Your Neighborhood"})

viewof dateWrittenV = Inputs.datetime({label: "Date Written", value: "2024-02-26", max: "2026-02-26"})
